{"prompt": "Generate a website for a smart home technology. The website should be sleek and use red as the brand color.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Smart Home Tech</title>\n    <style>\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            background-color: #f4f4f4;\n            color: #333;\n            line-height: 1.6;\n        }\n        header {\n            background-color: #c0392b; /* Red brand color */\n            color: #ffffff;\n            padding: 20px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n        }\n        header h1 {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 2.5em;\n            letter-spacing: 2px;\n        }\n        .container {\n            width: 80%;\n            margin: 20px auto;\n            overflow: hidden;\n            padding: 20px;\n            background-color: #ffffff;\n            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n            border-radius: 8px;\n        }\n        .hero {\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 50px 20px;\n            background-color: #e74c3c; /* Slightly lighter red */\n            color: #ffffff;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n        }\n        .hero h2 {\n            font-size: 2.2em;\n            margin-bottom: 15px;\n            letter-spacing: 1px;\n        }\n        .hero p {\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n            max-width: 700px;\n            margin: 0 auto;\n        }\n        .features {\n            display: grid;\n            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));\n            gap: 20px;\n            margin-top: 30px;\n        }\n        .feature-item {\n            background-color: #f9f9f9;\n            padding: 20px;\n            border-left: 5px solid #c0392b; /* Red accent */\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            text-align: center;\n            transition: transform 0.2s ease-in-out, box-shadow 0.2s ease-in-out;\n        }\n        .feature-item:hover {\n            transform: translateY(-5px);\n            box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n        }\n        .feature-item h3 {\n            color: #c0392b; /* Red brand color */\n            margin-top: 0;\n            font-size: 1.4em;\n        }\n        footer {\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 20px;\n            margin-top: 40px;\n            background-color: #333;\n            color: #ffffff;\n        }\n        footer p {\n            margin: 0;\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n    <header>\n        <h1>SmartHome Hub</h1>\n    </header>\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <section class=\"hero\">\n            <h2>Experience the Future of Home Living</h2>\n            <p>Seamlessly connect and control your devices for ultimate comfort, security, and efficiency. Your intelligent home starts here.</p>\n        </section>\n\n        <section class=\"features\">\n            <div class=\"feature-item\">\n                <h3>Intelligent Lighting</h3>\n                <p>Automate your lights based on your schedule or presence. Save energy and set the perfect ambiance.</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"feature-item\">\n                <h3>Climate Control</h3>\n                <p>Maintain your ideal temperature effortlessly. Smart thermostats learn your preferences and optimize energy usage.</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"feature-item\">\n                <h3>Enhanced Security</h3>\n                <p>Monitor your home from anywhere with smart cameras, sensors, and smart locks. Receive instant alerts.</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"feature-item\">\n                <h3>Voice Integration</h3>\n                <p>Control all your devices with simple voice commands. Compatible with major voice assistants.</p>\n            </div>\n        </section>\n    </div>\n    <footer>\n        <p>&copy; 2023 SmartHome Hub. All rights reserved.</p>\n    </footer>\n</body>\n</html>\n"}